\[\iint\|T_{\varepsilon}^{\mu\to\rho}(x)-T_{\varepsilon}^{\mu^{\prime}\to\rho}( x^{\prime})\|\mathrm{d}\pi(x,x^{\prime})\leq\frac{2R^{2}}{\varepsilon}W_{2}(\mu,\mu^{ \prime})\,,\]

which completes the claim. 

